give @s minecraft:written_book[minecraft:written_book_content={title:"Comet Croft Field Guide",author:"Comet Croft",pages:["Comet Croft\n\nA croft is a small\nhomestead. This\none is yours.\n\nFarm through real\nseasons. Build it\nup, room by room.\nAnd watch the sky.","When you meet an\nitem you don't\nknow: open your\ninventory, hover\nit, press R.\n\nThat shows how\nit's made. And U\nshows its uses.","The homestead\n\nGrab a hoe and\ntill some soil.\nPlant what you\nfind and let it\ngrow.\n\nThen build a\nkitchen and cook\na real meal.","The turning year\n\nCrops keep to the\nseasons. Plant in\nspring and summer.\nPut food by for\nwinter, when\nlittle grows.\n\nThe leaves and sky\ntell you where you\nare in the year.","The falling sky\n\nSome nights the\nsky sends a comet\ndown. You'll hear\nit land.\n\nWalk out to the\ncrater to see\nwhat it left.\n\nA spyglass helps\nyou watch for\nmore.","Finding your way\n\nBind a waystone\nand you can jump\nback to it from\nany other.\n\nKeep a map and a\nbackpack on you.\nThe world is wide\nand worth the walk.","Last thing\n\nThat's enough to\nstart. Everything\nelse you can learn\nby pressing R on it."]}]
